FT  08 JUL 93 / Observer: For the high jump
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
After the empire, manufacturing and moral values, is the British officer
class now also on the decline? That at any rate is the perception of Major
General Rob McAfee, in charge of army training.
He went before the Commons defence committee yesterday to bemoan the
